# Pet Circle — User Story Map

Last updated: 2026-03-05 (after commits `61a0965`, `58653b0`)

## Update Protocol

After completing work on any user story listed below:
1. Change its status to reflect the new state (DONE / PARTIAL / MISSING)
2. Update the counts in the Summary section
3. Move resolved PARTIAL items to the DONE section
4. Add any newly discovered gaps to the appropriate section

---

## Status: DONE (36 stories)

These stories are fully functional in the current mock-data mode.

### Authentication & Onboarding
- A1: Welcome screen with sign-up and sign-in buttons
- A2: Role selection (Vet / Pet Owner)
- A3–A7: Email auth, Google, Apple, password reset (behind Firebase flag)
- A8–A10: Email verification with resend and account switch (behind Firebase flag)
- B1: Onboarding Step 1 — name, breed, age persisted to `petStore`
- B3: Onboarding Step 3 — target rate saved to `settingsStore`

### Owner Experience
- B5: Owner dashboard with pet cards from `petStore` + empty state CTA
- B6: Pet card tap navigates to pet detail
- B7: Quick-action Measure / Trends buttons per pet
- B8: Manual tap-to-count with haptics and BPM calculation
- B9: Configurable timer durations (15s / 30s / 60s)
- B10: "Add to Graph" saves measurement via `measurementStore`
- B13: Medication save wired to `medicationStore`
- B14: Export measurement data — CSV preview dialog (no file download)
- B15: Pet detail reads from `noteStore` and `measurementStore`
- B16: "View Graph" navigates to trends tab
- B17: Notifications from `notificationStore` with tap-to-mark-read
- B18: Dark mode toggle
- B19: Language switcher (EN / HE)
- B20: SRR thresholds saved to `settingsStore`
- B21: Care circle invite dialog from settings
- B22: Export all data dialog from settings
- B23: Share with vet dialog from settings
- B24: Push / emergency notification toggles wired to `settingsStore`

### Vet Experience
- C1: Clinic overview dashboard from stores with real stats
- C2: Summary stats (normal / elevated / measurements) from stores
- C3: Patient card tap navigates to pet detail
- C4: Clinical notes persisted via `noteStore`
- C6: Notifications from `notificationStore`

### Caregiver
- D2: Take measurements (same as B8–B10)
- D3: View pet details (same as B15)

### Cross-Cutting
- E1: Persistent tab navigation (Home, Trends, Measure, Messages)
- E2: Settings drawer from avatar tap
- E3: Notifications drawer from bell icon
- E4: RTL layout for Hebrew
- E5: Full dark mode support

---

## Status: PARTIAL (7 stories)

These have UI but are incomplete or missing data wiring.

| ID | Story | Gap | File |
|----|-------|-----|------|
| B2 | Onboarding diagnosis | Collected in Step 2 but `Pet` model has no `diagnosis` field — data is lost | `onboarding_step2.dart`, `pet.dart` |
| B4 | Onboarding care circle invites | Emails collected but never converted to `CareCircleMember` objects | `onboarding_flow.dart` |
| B11 | Trends SRR chart | Reads from `measurementStore` but falls back to hardcoded Jan 3–9 data when empty | `trends_screen.dart` |
| B12 | Trends time filter | Period dropdown changes state but no filtering logic applies to chart data | `trends_screen.dart` |
| C5 | Vet SRR trends | Same as B11 | `trends_screen.dart` |
| D1 | Caregiver dashboard | Screen exists with store data but has NO ROUTE — unreachable | `care_circle_dashboard.dart` |
| M9 | Care circle management | Invite works but no remove, role change, or pending invite UI | `settings_screen.dart` |

---

## Status: MISSING (9 stories — Phase 1 gaps)

No implementation exists. These should be built before Phase 2.

| ID | Story | Notes |
|----|-------|-------|
| M1 | Add pet after onboarding | No "Add Pet" button post-onboarding; `petStore.addPet` exists |
| M2 | Edit pet profile | Pet detail is read-only; `petStore.updatePet` exists |
| M3 | Delete / archive pet | `petStore.removePet` exists but no UI |
| M4 | Select pet to measure | `measurement_screen.dart` hardcodes `ownerPets.first` |
| M5 | Switch active pet context | `AppHeader` has `onPetSelectorTap` but `MainShell` doesn't wire it |
| M6 | User profile management | No way to edit name or photo; `userService.updateUser` exists |
| M7 | Sign out from main app | Only available on verify-email screen |
| M8 | Caregiver route / role | `CareCircleDashboard` exists but no route, no role option |
| M10 | Measurement deletion | No store method or UI to remove a reading |

---

## Status: FUTURE (16 stories — Phase 2–5)

| Phase | Stories |
|-------|---------|
| 2 | Firebase Auth production, Firestore persistence, real-time sync, push notifications (FCM), care circle invitation flow |
| 3 | VisionRR camera measurement, trend anomaly detection, automated SRR alerts, measurement reminders, vet-to-owner messaging |
| 4 | PDF report generation, CSV file export, shareable health summaries, vet clinic analytics |
| 5 | Apple Watch / WearOS companion, offline mode with sync |

---

## Recommended Next Priorities

1. Fix onboarding gaps (B2, B4) — add `diagnosis` to Pet model, convert emails to members
2. Complete trends (B11, B12) — remove hardcoded fallback, add time-range filtering
3. Add pet switcher (M5) — wire `onPetSelectorTap` in MainShell
4. Add "Add Pet" flow (M1) — button on owner dashboard
5. Add sign out (M7) — add to settings drawer
6. Add caregiver route (M8) — register route, enable caregiver role
7. Pet measurement selector (M4) — pick which pet before measuring
8. Edit pet profile (M2) — edit mode on pet detail screen

